Class MutableMapping<T extends @Nullable Object>

java.lang.Object
com.ibm.wala.util.intset.MutableMapping<T>
All Implemented Interfaces:
OrdinalSetMapping<T>, Serializable, Iterable<T>
Direct Known Subclasses:
UnorderedDomain
public class MutableMapping<T extends @Nullable Object> extends Object implements OrdinalSetMapping<T>, Serializable
A bit set mapping based on an object array. This is not terribly efficient, but is useful for prototyping.
